headline: Universal Health Services (UHS) Upgraded to Buy: Here's Why
summary: Universal Health Services (UHS) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company's earnings prospects. This might drive the stock higher in the near term.

headline: Does Universal Health Services (UHS) Have the Potential to Rally 26.33% as Wall Street Analysts Expect?
summary: The mean of analysts' price targets for Universal Health Services (UHS) points to a 26.3% upside in the stock. While this highly sought-after metric has not proven reasonably effective, strong agreement among analysts in raising earnings estimates does indicate an upside in the stock.
